{"tid":1607072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日10月1日 賀國慶","createTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:29:13.000Z","uid":94915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3cbf486772013c1b7078a297cce9b51143b046","tid":1607072,"uid":94915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我屌你老母 今日係港殤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n6月頭，呢場運動流第一滴血𠴱陣已經有用黑洋紫荊旗，手足仲升埋旗，但好似未有人正式講過<br />\n我而家就宣佈，呢支黑洋紫荊旗係我地嘅 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n港。殤。旗 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Remembrance Flag</span></span></strong></span>！！<br />\n紀念嘅係我地不論勇和喺戰場喺狗屋流過嘅每一滴血，失去過嘅每一位手足，紀念香港人抗爭嘅每一年每一日！<br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaHqWAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaHqWAY.jpg&h=c4deb4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但記唔記得點解可以有嗰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5粒星</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！！我地一路反共反支一路又用番污染咗嘅洋紫荊make唔make sense啊！！？？？？粒星代表<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n要用就用純白花！港殤啊！去共啊！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZpkLtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZpkLtE.jpg&h=0d7f08e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼全部人同我print定堆張離出黎 10月1 fing 爆佢連儂牆貼爆佢啊！<br />\n當榮光歸香港，我地會有一支真正屬於我地嘅旗，唔L係共紅色嗰支啊。到時後呢一支 Rememberance Flag 就係用離紀念我地嘅勝利，嗰日離之前我地就高舉我地嘅黑旗克L死共匪！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xob7tkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXob7tkq.jpg&h=ec396985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bHB565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bHB565.jpg&h=4a3176bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HyxEr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HyxEr6.jpg&h=8523a959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPv8cM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPv8cM7.jpg&h=c7fa7449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiNB568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiNB568.jpg&h=cd92ac86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NS6SEr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNS6SEr9.jpg&h=4dd00a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z189GFv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ189GFv.jpg&h=80be5a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U7EpvKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU7EpvKe.png&h=98f8a688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[10.1賀佢老母] 呢一支先係真真正正屬於我地香港人嘅旗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605241</a>"},{"pid":"b5672ad0e12ce924ba9ad4f4fce777fe3e9a9bd6","tid":1607072,"uid":94915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"26aa9496a82b8dac94e0282bed1a77d706dd56c6","tid":1607072,"uid":94915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:42.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c4162bd2ebabe9eb1b61d7097b2f518f9adf5ec6","tid":1607072,"uid":94915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"b0ad786b5e8479ce18e4578209b5d4da0e3f7bdd","tid":1607072,"uid":94915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:25:03.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"646e770fe52faecfa50a4a7efbca1a15c1aff804","tid":1607072,"uid"